definition.achievementDescription: §dUltimate - (Ability 5) When on the Peak of your power,  attacking your enemy will create a strong connection between you and your target, allowing a strong electrical current flow directly to his nervous system, hurting you a bit in exchange for extreme damage on the opponent. Requires Power Level 5. Cooldown: 40 Minutes
